    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 has been reviewed and accepted as a complete record of the current state of evidence, notwithstanding the Not Accepted regulatory decision on the underlying model. The assessment package documents all 13 credibility factors, identifies 6 epistemic gaps at MRL 5, and provides a traceable Monte Carlo UQ record. Acceptance of this UoA package reflects acceptance of the assessment process and documentation, not acceptance of the model for regulatory submission. The package is filed as the basis for a gap-closure roadmap.",
